---
title: Buttery Sauteed Peas Peas Sauteed with Shallot, Garlic and Butter
description: Green garden peas are a vibrant addition to any dish, and this recipe sees them sauteed with plenty of butter to make it a truly special side. Fried gently with shallot, garlic and a dash of lemon juice, these are anything but ordinary peas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61825dafc0e70439911a15b9-322d59fd.jpg
